OL,3,CBoy denies the murder of 16-year-old
OL,4,Cstudent
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has denied murdering
OL,7,Fa 16-year-old student in Wiltshire.
OL,9,FThe youth, who cannot be identified
OL,10,Fbecause of his age, appeared before
OL,11,FBristol Crown Court on Thursday 2
OL,12,FApril charged with murdering Shayne
OL,13,FHambakachere.
OL,15,FShayne, a Year 11 pupil, was found
OL,16,Fseriously injured on London Road in
OL,17,FChippenham shortly before 4pm on 31
OL,18,FJanuary 2026.
OL,20,FHe was taken to Southmead Hospital in
OL,21,FBristol, where he died.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
