OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775235955
OL,3,CBoy denies the murder of 16-year-old
OL,4,Cstudent
OL,6,FJudge Anna Richardson told the
OL,7,Fdefendant that he would remain in
OL,8,Fyouth detention ahead of his trial on
OL,9,F10 August.
OL,11,FThe boy spoke to confirm his name and
OL,12,Freply "not guilty" after the charge of
OL,13,Fmurder was read to him.
OL,15,F"You know that your case is listed for
OL,16,Ftrial on 10 August," the judge told
OL,17,Fhim.
OL,26,@tD@GOUtD@RO]wD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
