OL,3,CBoy denies the murder of 16-year-old
OL,4,Cstudent
OL,6,F"Your next court hearing is going to
OL,7,Fbe on 20 May. In the meantime, you
OL,8,Fwill remain remanded to the youth
OL,9,Fdetention accommodation."
OL,11,FThe trial is expected to last two
OL,12,Fweeks.
OL,14,FA reporting restriction was previously
OL,15,Fput in place to prohibit publication
OL,16,Fof details likely to lead to the
OL,17,Fidentification of the defendant.
OL,19,FSarah Jones KC appeared for the
OL,20,Fprosecution and Alex Daymond
OL,21,Frepresented the defendant.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@YO]
