OL,3,CBoy denies the murder of 16-year-old
OL,4,Cstudent
OL,6,FShayne's father, Emmanuel
OL,7,FHambakachere, previously paid tribute
OL,8,Fto his son in a statement released by
OL,9,FWiltshire Police.
OL,11,F"At home he made sure he would do his
OL,12,Fchores on a daily basis, he always
OL,13,Fcame home before his curfew and always
OL,14,Fcommunicated every time he left the
OL,15,Fhouse or came back," he said.
OL,17,F"He was very helpful around the house
OL,18,Fand did whatever was asked of him
OL,19,Fwithout complaining. He was also very
OL,20,Fsmart and tidy, he would not leave for
OL,21,Fschool without making his bed.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@TO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775235955
OL,3,CBoy denies the murder of 16-year-old
OL,4,Cstudent
OL,6,F"Shayne was a brave and bold young
OL,7,Fman, he was never afraid to speak his
OL,8,Fmind or to stand up for what he
OL,9,Fbelieved in."
OL,11,FFlowers and tributes were left at
OL,12,FHardenhuish School in Chippenham,
OL,13,Fwhere Shayne was a pupil.
OL,15,FIn a statement, the school said: "The
OL,16,FHardenhuish School community is deeply
OL,17,Fsaddened by the tragic loss of one of
OL,18,Four Year 11 students, Shayne
OL,19,FHambakachere, following an incident in
OL,20,FChippenham on Saturday.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@MO]wD@bOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
