OL,3,CBoy denies the murder of 16-year-old
OL,4,Cstudent
OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with his family and
OL,7,Ffriends at this sad time.
OL,9,F"We are taking the time to remember
OL,10,Fthis wonderful young person who had
OL,11,Fsuch a promising life ahead and to
OL,12,Fsupport our whole community in coming
OL,13,Fto terms with his loss and this tragic
OL,14,Fevent."
